						               													<description>Battle on the high seas or in the crowded streets of the Spanish Main as a Pirate, Pirate Hunter or a simple Merchant in this minatures game!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Using the Chain Reaction System found in all of Two Hour Wargames, you field a group of characters with very simple stats: Reputation and Weapons.  Activation rolls tell you when you are able to go (higher rolls go first, but only activate higher Reputation groups) and then you may move and fire/charge.  That's it!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Of course, being the reaction system, the other figures on the board won't be sitting and waiting for you to finish in a IGO-UGO fashion, but will react to your moves using a series of tables that may have them running from you, drawing pistols and firing, or charging into combat swords shining!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Be the last pirate standing and win!&amp;#10;Or play a campaign and retire with the most gold to win!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Rules to adventure ashore?Check!&amp;#10;Big Land Battles to sack Panama? Check!&amp;#10;Ship combat with boarding actions? Check!&amp;#10;Big Sea Battles to fight fleets? Check!&amp;#10;Treasure maps and buried treasure? Check!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
